        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "ῥαπισμὸς",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " a stroke on the face. The p petrators of these outrages in Mk. are ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "τινὲς",
